        {
            "title": "港股開市︱重越二萬六 恒指漲209點報26177點 中美元首下周會面利好市場氣氛",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中美兩國元首將於下周四在南韓會面，為港股再添反彈動力。恒生指數今早開市報26177點，升209點或0.81%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250424_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250424_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報6032點，升80點或1.36%；國企指數以9380點開市，升79點或0.86%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股普遍造好，阿里巴巴(09988)開報168元，升2.07%；騰訊(00700)開報639元，升0.95%；昨天重拾「紅底股」資格的美團(03690)今早開報101.3元，升1.3%；京東(09618)開報129.7元，升0.78%；小米(01810)開報47.1元，升0.77%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-101723__source-web_09988-8_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-101723__source-web_09988-8_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩大重磅金融股則個別發展，滙控(00005)開報102.6元，逆市跌0.1%；友邦(01299)開報71.4元，升0.71%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">普拉達(01913)今年首9個月收益淨額按年升8.9%，所有地區零售均有增長；該股今早開報47.9元，升3.46%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：普拉達2024年度年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250402_FI_source-web_01913.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：普拉達2024年度年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250402_FI_source-web_01913.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：普拉達2024年度年報</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今早共有3家公司獲提私有化或全購，股份今早復牌互有升跌。五礦地產(00230)獲溢價1.04倍私有化，該股今早應聲飆91.84%，開報0.94元；康大食品(00834)獲溢價16.23%提全購，該股今早開報0.6元，大漲1.63倍；俊裕地基(01757)獲折讓79.06%提全購，股份今早開報0.5元，亦升17.65%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15367238-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a%e4%ba%8c%e8%90%ac%e5%85%ad-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e6%bc%b2209%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126177%e9%bb%9e-%e4%b8%ad%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e9%a6%96%e4%b8%8b",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 09:30:28",
